<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product 1 Details</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .product-image {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .product-image img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

        .product-details {
            text-align: left;
        }

            .product-details h2 {
                margin: 10px 0;
                font-size: 24px;
                color: #333;
            }

            .product-details p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #666;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .product-details .price {
                font-size: 20px;
                color: #007bff;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .product-details button {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                cursor: pointer;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

                .product-details button:hover {
                    background-color: #0056b3;
                }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

            .back-button:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Product 1 Details</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="product-image">
            <img src="https://cf.shopee.vn/file/sg-11134201-7rd6m-lwbi3j3acfmla3" alt="Product 1">
        </div>
        <div class="product-details">
            <h2>Product 1</h2>
            <p>Here is a detailed description of Product 1. It includes all the features and benefits of the product, providing potential buyers with all the information they need.</p>
            <div class="price">$19.99</div>
            <button>Add to Cart</button>
            <a href="index.html" class="back-button">Back to Store</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
